Batman Forever;;32;;38;;PG-13;;Batman (Val Kilmer) faces off against two foes: the schizophrenic, horribly scarred former District Attorney Harvey Dent, aka Two-Face (Tommy Lee Jones), and the Riddler (Jim Carrey), a disgruntled ex-Wayne Enterprises inventor seeking revenge against his former employer by unleashing his brain-sucking weapon on Gotham City's residents. As the caped crusader also deals with tortured memories of his parents' murder, he has a new romance, with psychologist Chase Meridian (Nicole Kidman).;;Fantasy,Adventure,Action;;Joel Schumacher;;1995;;Val Kilmer,Tommy Lee Jones,Jim Carrey,Nicole Kidman,Chris O'Donnell,Michael Gough,Pat Hingle,Drew Barrymore,Debi Mazar,Ed Begley Jr.;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/batman_forever